{"tid":2226409,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海上長征六小時 違法船隻一籮籮","createTime":"2020-10-02T04:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T05:00:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d773e7649361913e7b5050b06793e3ef58b19a09","tid":2226409,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201002/QSDEPCBZORAMZKTVXI7OFUNSBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201002%2FQSDEPCBZORAMZKTVXI7OFUNSBE%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAnqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=c3fa46be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201002%2FQSDEPCBZORAMZKTVXI7OFUNSBE%2F&h=d8e901be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201002/QSDEPCBZORAMZKTVXI7OFUNSBE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n海上長征六小時 違法船隻一籮籮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6TJMaX2O22SlTG1ucYVrBxtxPlE=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U7GRVIUTLBBAVJ3WVUZRAR6GIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6TJMaX2O22SlTG1ucYVrBxtxPlE%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU7GRVIUTLBBAVJ3WVUZRAR6GIA.jpg&h=bc46dfeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■本報記者連日出海，考察12港人出航路線。馬泉崇攝<br />\n<br />\n【採訪手記】記者日前模擬12人出海情況，當天天氣與8.23相若，並約定船家早上7時許開船，雖然預定航線不會超越香港水域範圍，並確定肯定合法和安全，但凌晨在家收拾裝備之際，心中突然驚覺「好似執緊嘢着草」，朋友知悉有關採訪工作，有人再三好言奉勸，甚至追問「畀公安越境捉咗點算？」家人問及「聽日咁早去邊？」時，記者為免引來擔心，選擇了支吾以對。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警突棄巡布袋澳  村民質疑「放人出海」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。船家說：「一來當日天氣唔大風浪，同埋打風前少啲（水警）巡邏嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n船家：打風前出發係好時機<br />\n<br />\n經歷過去一年多的反送中運動，陸上採訪「大長征」已成常態，海上長征記者卻是新手。清晨的布袋澳較記者想像熱鬧，最少有村民游早水，亦已有人較記者更早乘「大飛」出公海「違法」潛水，因為目的地屬中國水域的擔桿島一帶，那到公海釣魚潛水其實需要申請嗎？船家說：「梗係冇牌啦，但個個都係咁出去。」原來，非法越境根本是常見之事。<br />\n<br />\n記者上船後回望布袋澳，留在視線最後的「地標」是村內海鮮酒家的招牌，或者也是12人望向香港的最後一瞥。。。。。。。。。。。。。既然海上「違法」船隻眾多，何以12人那一艘會在海警眼中「突圍而出」？記者嘗試從大海找答案，找到的卻是更多疑問。"},{"pid":"7825de2f72dcf92ce4f0af985c330d1aa1bb02a7","tid":2226409,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T04:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3e03365b0ed45140316fad2342447576e44787","tid":2226409,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:00:10.000Z","msg":"海軍死咗去邊？"}]}